        <h1 class="page-title">Button</h1>
        <p class="page-desc">
          The Button is the primary interactive element for triggering actions. It supports multiple visual variants for semantic meaning, four sizes for layout flexibility, and five interaction states.
        </p>
        <nav class="content-tabs">
          <button class="tab-item active">Overview</button>
          <button class="tab-item">Style</button>
          <button class="tab-item">Usage</button>
          <button class="tab-item">Code</button>
          <button class="tab-item">Accessibility</button>
        </nav>
      </div>
